  26.6.72 ESMF_FieldSync - Synchronize DEs across the Field in case of sharing

   INTERFACE:
   subroutine ESMF_FieldSync(field, rc)

   ARGUMENTS:
     type(ESMF_Field), intent(in)            :: field
 -- The following arguments require argument keyword syntax (e.g. rc=rc). --
     integer,          intent(out), optional :: rc

   DESCRIPTION:

   Synchronizes access to DEs across field to make sure PETs correctly
   access the data for read and write when DEs are shared.

   The arguments are:

   field
          Specified ESMF_Field object.

   [rc]
          Return code; equals ESMF_SUCCESS if there are no errors.

